{"id":271,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":271,"title":"Revelation 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","John sees the book sealed with seven seals, and he sees those people redeemed out of every nation—He hears every creature praising God and the Lamb."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.1","order":"03.29.005.27448"},["b","1"],"And I saw in the right hand of him that sat on the throne a book",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"written"],"within and on the backside,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"sealed"],"with seven",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"seals"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.2","order":"03.29.005.27449"},["b","2"],"And I saw a strong angel proclaiming with a loud voice, Who is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"worthy"],"to open the book, and to loose the seals thereof?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.3","order":"03.29.005.27450"},["b","3"],"And no man in heaven, nor in earth, neither under the earth, was able to open the book, neither to look thereon."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.4","order":"03.29.005.27451"},["b","4"],"And I wept much, because no man was found worthy to open and to read the book, neither to look thereon."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.5","order":"03.29.005.27452"},["b","5"],"And one of the elders saith unto me, Weep not: behold, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Lion"],"of the tribe of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Juda"],", the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"Root"],"of David, hath prevailed to open the book, and to loose the seven seals thereof."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.6","order":"03.29.005.27453"},["b","6"],"And I beheld, and, lo, in the midst of the throne and of the four beasts, and in the midst of the elders, stood a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Lamb"],"as it had been slain,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"having"],"seven horns and seven eyes, which are the seven Spirits of God sent forth into all the earth."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.7","order":"03.29.005.27454"},["b","7"],"And he came and took the book out of the right hand of him that sat upon the throne."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.8","order":"03.29.005.27455"},["b","8"],"And when he had taken the book, the four beasts and four",["i","and"],"twenty elders fell down before the Lamb, having every one of them harps, and golden vials full of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"odours"],", which are the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"prayers"],"of saints."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.9","order":"03.29.005.27456"},["b","9"],"And they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sung"],"a new song, saying, Thou art worthy to take the book, and to open the seals thereof: for thou wast slain, and hast",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"redeemed"],"us to God by thy blood out of every",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"kindred"],", and tongue, and people, and nation;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.10","order":"03.29.005.27457"},["b","10"],"And hast made us unto our God kings and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"priests"],": and we shall reign on the earth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.11","order":"03.29.005.27458"},["b","11"],"And I beheld, and I heard the voice of many angels round about the throne and the beasts and the elders: and the number of them was ten thousand times ten thousand, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"thousands"],"of thousands;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.12","order":"03.29.005.27459"},["b","12"],"Saying with a loud voice, Worthy is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Lamb"],"that was slain to receive",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"power"],", and riches, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"wisdom"],", and strength, and honour, and glory, and blessing."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.13","order":"03.29.005.27460"},["b","13"],"And every",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"creature"],"which is in heaven, and on the earth, and under the earth, and such as are in the sea, and all that are in them, heard I saying, Blessing, and honour, and glory, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"power"],",",["i","be"],"unto him that sitteth upon the throne, and unto the Lamb for ever and ever."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.14","order":"03.29.005.27461"},["b","14"],"And the four beasts said, Amen. And the four",["i","and"],"twenty elders fell down and worshipped him that liveth for ever and ever."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.1a","order":"03.29.005.27462"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/2.9.9-10"},"Ezek. 2:9 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.1b","order":"03.29.005.27464"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.6"},"D&C 77:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.1c","order":"03.29.005.27466"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seal"},"TG Seal"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.2a","order":"03.29.005.27468"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worthiness"},"TG Worthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.5a","order":"03.29.005.27470"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.9"},"Gen. 49:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.5b","order":"03.29.005.27472"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-judah-people-of"},"TG Israel, Judah, People of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.5c","order":"03.29.005.27474"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.10"},"Isa. 11:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.16.6-16"},"Rev. 22:16 (6–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.6a","order":"03.29.005.27476"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-types-of-in-anticipation"},"TG Jesus Christ, Types of, in Anticipation"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.6b","order":"03.29.005.27478"},["b","6b"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 5:6 … having",["i","twelve"],"horns and",["i","twelve"],"eyes, which are the",["i","twelve servants"],"of God, sent forth into all the earth."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.8a","order":"03.29.005.27480"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"incense."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.8b","order":"03.29.005.27482"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/23.13"},"1 Chr. 23:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/141.2"},"Ps. 141:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/8.4.3-4"},"Rev. 8:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.9a","order":"03.29.005.27484"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/singing"},"TG Singing"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.9b","order":"03.29.005.27486"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"},"TG Jesus Christ, Redeemer"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/redemption"},"Redemption"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.9c","order":"03.29.005.27488"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/7.9"},"Rev. 7:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.10a","order":"03.29.005.27490"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priest-aaronic-priesthood"},"TG Priest, Aaronic Priesthood"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/priests"},"BD Priests"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.11a","order":"03.29.005.27492"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/7.10"},"Dan. 7:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.12a","order":"03.29.005.27494"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lamb-of-god"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lamb of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.12b","order":"03.29.005.27496"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Authority of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.12c","order":"03.29.005.27498"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-wisdom-of"},"TG God, Wisdom of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.13a","order":"03.29.005.27500"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.104"},"D&C 88:104"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/5.13b","order":"03.29.005.27502"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-power-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Power of"],"."]]}
